# Response Style Preferences

## No Summaries
- Do NOT generate summary sections at the end of responses
- Do NOT create recap or "what was done" sections
- Just do the work and move on

## No Documentation
- Do NOT create documentation files (.md, README, guides) unless explicitly requested
- Do NOT create SETUP.md, IMPLEMENTATION.md, GUIDE.md, etc.
- Only create docs when user specifically asks for documentation

## Concise Communication
- Keep responses brief and to the point
- Focus on the actual work, not explanations
- Let the code speak for itself
